Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島上的男人們每年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會舉辦只有男人參加的大船捕魚大會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在12年前的大會時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現了百年難見的大浪襲擊了小島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人們都被漂流到了島嶼之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這個島上沒有一個男人的緣由？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  不過只是從婆婆那裡聽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  那大浪再來的話就能出島了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但婆婆說那是百年難得一見的大浪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算來的時候  下次也會在…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,107年後？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我覺得你這計算錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎  奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此等下去  也會變成爺爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  今天發生了許多  行人也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡…睡是…在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人可以先睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗下澡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:03.01,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被圍追的  女婿殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以後會變成怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於離開父親  獲得自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是堅強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然從父親那裡獲得了自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請自由的對待我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:27.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自在別人家做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得讓行人住在這樣破舊狹窄骯髒的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過藍蘭島的第一個夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴  別管這些  快點穿衣服  衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不得不和你做個決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論試幾次做結果都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決斷什麼的就算了  鈴  快穿衣服  衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  為什麼會把這說成是別人的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說無益！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  快穿衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  都怎麼了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡十二年的女人本能覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心過來看看居然是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話就只能用「那個」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚這男人由我保管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉擇是在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用爭奪女婿殿下捉迷藏大會決出勝負～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豎日早上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我不得不成為女婿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人一個都沒有  現在要滅亡之時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你漂流到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是天命了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼年輕就結婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四  十五歲結婚是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管以前還是現在都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相愛的人能在一起就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和年齡沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不在這裡決定你屬於誰的話  就停止不了騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我又不是東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相成為對方的東西  結婚不就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要這樣的婚姻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會說那種偉大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不單是一個  全部都成為新娘的話怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣人口也會增加  正好得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣你就會很辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受  我接受了就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只有堂堂正正的甩掉她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該誰都不用選了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪女婿大人的躲藏大會開幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則有三條
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  範圍只是島的西邊  特別是東邊的森林不能進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  時限到夕陽沉入水平線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  最先碰到女婿殿下的人是勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  對體力還是有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以女人的腳力能追上我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  這樣下去會被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道發生什麼  趁現在快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子決出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和她有關係才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算甩開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去絕對能逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找東西的話要到高處最好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說登高的本領  我是最厲害的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的這些事情真是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也做了那麼美妙的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天雖然有點大意  今天沒那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在很急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是怎麼回事——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  新娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是很憧憬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且結婚的話  那些纏我的傢伙也會消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（很受同性歡迎的類型）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場勝負  我贏定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了什麼氣息…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你藏到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對結婚沒有興趣  請安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎  真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對地  對男性這種生物卻有很深的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…難道是陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  那邊有連這島上最博學的我都沒看見過的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶有傳說氣息的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會讓身體變大的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人就成為我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我從每寸肌膚和那個身體生態研究吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧  千影小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}（自作自受）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到  發現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來為什麼會有這種體力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為什麼每天不得不遭遇這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會放棄  難得脫離父親得到的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然遇上了一條河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫町
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女子不才  請指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  就這樣輸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓住  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要…決斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  現在不是做這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:11:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣的河應該會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹鷹？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個不會讓給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紋次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:06.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}（鴕鳥  不會飛）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨鳥  那麼華麗的登場之後居然是這副蠢樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想點什麼辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到女婿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃就能作為出色的大人  被大家承認了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我應該掉下瀑布懸崖了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…在飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下來  放我下來  我在高處是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別亂動  別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的放我下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  糟糕了  到東邊的森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  是風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  行人和炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東邊的森林是全是食肉植物的危險地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是什麼島
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那裡有比食肉植物更加可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東邊森林之主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行人被發現之前  不救出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回  又是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我以後會小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  我還在想會是什麼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是可愛的熊貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是說  生氣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了  現在正在捉迷藏中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴也參加大賽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會想讓我成為女婿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然救我很感謝  但是不逃離這裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西邊的懸崖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西邊的懸崖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日一定要做決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪女婿捉迷藏大會…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕…夕陽還沒沉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然很想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明擺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不甘心的鈴面前抓住的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很爽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人特製的麻痹藥怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你也不能動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子決出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣對鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始鈴在什麼大會都是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相比我每次都最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是在妨礙別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最火大的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明前一陣子裡還和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼短時間內就超越我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是壓倒性的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我喜歡就讓它變大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…就是理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是用今天的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能勾銷至今的全部失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個島唯一的男人成為我的僕人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的成為我的東西吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（真人）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  夕陽沉下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有好好的逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  我一直都監視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝者是——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候被鈴抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說一定要抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是碰到的就是贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險…險…險…險…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候確實你摸到鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:34.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（摸到那裡了嗎？）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  東邊的森林是範圍以外  應該不算…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多小孩就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情還是無法接受…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣很奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚是要和喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以行人和誰結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到行人的喜歡的人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個人相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的等著  有什麼不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷  這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼做  反正一生都離不開這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  為了增加友誼來我家吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來我家吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼都沒有解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我贏了  鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}來吧來吧  行人  今天開始…
